title: Blues Clues UK-1
description:
Step into the colourful, animated storybook world of Blue's Clues - where everyday objects come alive and young viewers are invited to help finish the day's adventures. Kevin Duala, the live action host, and his puppy Blue interact with viewers as they investigate, discover, solve puzzles and play games. <a href="
http://www.nickjr.co.uk/shows/blues/index.aspx" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.nickjr.co.uk/shows/blues/index.aspx</a>

Anatomy
Blue and Kevin find out about the parts of the body in today's exciting edition of Blue's Clues!


Animal Behaviour
Blue and Kevin explore the wide world of the animal kingdom, and discover that not all animals are the same.


Art Appreciation
Art isn't just something you'll find in the gallery - it's everywhere you look! Join Kevin and Blue as they appreciate the art in the world around us.


Blue Experiments
Blue and Kevin get scientifically minded as they take to the kitchen to discover what things float, what things sink, and other interesting experiments.
